[SIGHS]

03:42.483 --> 03:44.093
So we came to...

03:44.136 --> 03:49.490
We came to Detroit to talk
to young people, kids.

03:49.533 --> 03:53.711
You know, we came to Detroit
to talk to kids, young people,

03:54.538 --> 03:57.759
