50:05.350 --> 50:06.612
- Um...

50:08.135 --> 50:10.616
Viv, I'm so sorry, uh...

50:10.659 --> 50:12.748
- It's fine, it's fine.

50:12.792 --> 50:14.533
Um, just tell him I love
him and I miss him, okay?

50:14.576 --> 50:15.447
[SNIFFLING]

50:15.490 --> 50:16.709
- Okay.

50:16.752 --> 50:18.145
I'm gonna go get him.

50:21.627 --> 50:25.457
[OPERA MUSIC PLAYING]

50:42.604 --> 50:46.913
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

51:07.194 --> 51:09.979
- What's your child like,
you know,

51:10.023 --> 51:11.633
fighting about
washing his hair,

51:11.677 --> 51:14.723
'cause I could
do that anytime.

