51:37.529 --> 51:38.878
- Hmm, sorry about that.

51:39.444 --> 51:41.185
- It is harsh.

51:41.228 --> 51:43.665
Not even as a punishment, just,

51:43.709 --> 51:45.537
Wash your hair,
you dumb kids.

51:46.755 --> 51:47.930
- Yeah.

51:48.583 --> 51:49.845
What an awful place.

51:50.368 --> 51:51.586
- Yeah.

51:56.287 --> 51:58.376
- Okay. [INHALES]

51:58.419 --> 52:02.162
Do you want to fight
about washing your hair

