and lowered his ax.

52:34.368 --> 52:36.457
'This is a great
comfort,' he said.

52:36.501 --> 52:39.243
'I have been holding that ax
in the air ever since I rusted

52:39.286 --> 52:42.071
'and I'm glad to
put it down at last.

52:42.115 --> 52:43.943
'Now, if you will oil
the joints of my legs,

52:43.986 --> 52:46.206
'I shall be all
right once more.'

