So they oiled his legs

52:48.252 --> 52:50.167
until he could
move them freely,

52:50.210 --> 52:52.604
and he thanked them again
and again for his release.

52:55.259 --> 52:56.738
Are you guys still there?

52:56.782 --> 52:58.218
Keep reading, Mama.

52:58.914 --> 53:01.003
- Okay. [SMACKS LIPS]

53:01.047 --> 53:02.135
I might have
stood there always

53:02.179 --> 53:04.181
if you had not come
along, he said.

53:04.224 --> 53:05.791
How did you
happen to be here?

53:05.834 --> 53:07.271
We are on our way
to the Emerald City

53:07.314 --> 53:09.577
to see the great Oz,
she answered.

53:18.586 --> 53:21.198
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

53:21.241 --> 53:23.069
- So does he just like
walk in to a room

53:23.112 --> 53:24.984
