53:38.084 --> 53:41.130
I have to be open
and so I say,

53:41.174 --> 53:42.654
Hey, man, I know

53:42.697 --> 53:44.264
you wanna talk
about something?

53:44.308 --> 53:45.526
- Yeah.

53:45.570 --> 53:47.267
- And... Yeah, and I
look at him like this,

53:47.311 --> 53:48.442
like real earnest.

53:48.486 --> 53:49.878
- Yeah, sincere.

