54:07.113 --> 54:08.070
- No, he's gotta
find his own way!

54:08.114 --> 54:09.158
- Yes.

54:09.202 --> 54:10.116
- That's how we all did.

54:10.159 --> 54:15.382
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

54:16.165 --> 54:17.776
Let's say
somebody your age

54:17.819 --> 54:19.299
that was coming
from another...

54:19.343 --> 54:20.909
AnoYeah.y...

54:20.953 --> 54:23.738
What would you tell
them about the US?

54:23.782 --> 54:26.175
You come here and
you'll see a lot of bad,

54:26.219 --> 54:29.135
but it's beautiful.

54:29.178 --> 54:30.963
Even though there could be like
problems here and there,

54:31.006 --> 54:32.704
you know,

54:32.747 --> 54:34.923
you see all these good people
who just have kind hearts

54:34.967 --> 54:38.100
and, you know, and they
don't even know you.

54:39.406 --> 54:42.148
There's been a lot of
issues with my dad.

54:42.191 --> 54:43.976
He's in jail right now,

54:44.019 --> 54:47.762
so everything is,
like, crazy, you know?

54:47.806 --> 54:50.287
My little sister,
she didn't, like, really see

54:50.330 --> 54:51.853
what was actually going on.

54:51.897 --> 54:55.422
The stuff that I went
through, I don't want her

54:55.466 --> 54:57.424
to know any of
that or just be,

54:57.468 --> 54:59.774
like, have to
think about that.

54:59.818 --> 55:02.081
